{"tid":1314514,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲係鬼","createTime":"2019-07-14T08:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:50:49.000Z","uid":39808,"like":99,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b99f6f99ace0314ecb20e52ead712850ee7b2d54","tid":1314514,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">陳雲有幾咁癡線都好，都唔會唔知希特拉手勢在西方社會係原罪級別，仲話&quot;等外國媒體廣泛報導&quot;，話知你把口噏乜春，做咗手勢就只會被抺黑，其心可誅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZQHWZ1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZQHWZ1.gif&h=154bd205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲：有無示威者試過，集體用希特拉手勢，向黨衛軍敬禮，並且高呼「向盧偉聰特首問安，盧特首黨衛軍團萬歲」？<br />\n無囉。香港人，示威無幽默感。<br />\n英文是：&quot;Heil, Communist Army. Say hello to Chief Executive Lo.&quot; 做標語都得，等外國媒體廣泛報導，知道香港是軍閥政府統治。<br />\n和理非，有好多玩法。"},{"pid":"abe6b82991e428d3824cef63ada57dd1ab45d02b","tid":1314514,"uid":38904,"like":21,"dislike":6,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"陈云是狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecfc6b7532712ca7f5c178acfe762d915fcbd2c","tid":1314514,"uid":269683,"like":33,"dislike":6,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"有朋友fb有share 我都即刻屌柒佢<br />\n乜撚野幽默啊屌佢老味"},{"pid":"929e7c6f208efc7fbc55cdaadc2c46ff45690c2c","tid":1314514,"uid":37280,"like":18,"dislike":13,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"若是自稱是納粹就是原罪，但用來稱呼黑警不是<br />\n外國也有文章稱呼中國是納粹中國，沒有人覺得有問題"},{"pid":"6218ba94ec1cc65905880a25045cb52c7d9556e3","tid":1314514,"uid":277800,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"難得有人鬧熱普城"},{"pid":"f9ec000a896ebfbdd40e32539b174ec5fc454ebc","tid":1314514,"uid":202348,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"929e7c6f208efc7fbc55cdaadc2c46ff45690c2c","tid":1314514,"uid":37280,"like":18,"dislike":13,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-